title: How to pay electricity bill?
content: Go to Utilities > Select NEA > Enter SC Number and amount.

title: How to recharge mobile?
content: Select Mobile Recharge > Choose operator > Enter number and amount.

title: How to buy internet pack?
content: Navigate to Internet > Select provider > Enter username and amount.

title: How to pay water bill?
content: Go to Utilities > Select Khanepani > Enter customer ID and pay.

title: How to book a movie ticket?
content: Go to Tickets > Select QFX Cinemas > Choose show and seat.

title: How to pay for online shopping?
content: Go to Payments > Enter Daraz invoice ID > Confirm amount.

title: How to recharge Ncell?
content: Go to Mobile Recharge > Select Ncell > Enter number and confirm.

title: How to top-up Smart Cell?
content: Choose Mobile Recharge > Smart Cell > Enter number and amount.

title: Can I pay Subisu bills?
content: Yes, go to Internet section and choose Subisu.

title: Where to check transaction history?
content: Open Transaction tab in your profile menu.

title: Is eSewa safe?
content: Yes, it uses encrypted and secure transactions.

title: How to link bank account?
content: Go to Bank Link > Enter bank info > Verify with OTP.

title: Can I pay flight tickets?
content: Yes, go to Travel > Flight Booking.

title: How to cancel payment?
content: Open Transaction > Tap the payment > Choose cancel.

title: What is eSewa load?
content: It means adding funds to your eSewa wallet.

title: How to set auto-pay?
content: Go to Saved Templates > Enable auto-pay toggle.

title: How to use QR pay?
content: Open QR Scan > Scan merchant QR > Confirm payment.

title: Can I pay fuel bills?
content: Yes, select Nepal Oil Corporation under Utility.

title: What happens after failed payment?
content: Amount is refunded within 3 business days.

title: How to contact support?
content: Tap Help Center > Live Chat or call 1234.
